These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
Food: watermelon, lime, onion, peas
Nationality: brazilian, pakistani, polish, argentine
1. Nationality:pakistani is on the left of Nationality:brazilian##1
2. Food:watermelon == Nationality:argentine##1
3. Nationality:polish is on the right of Nationality:brazilian##1
4. Food:lime is on the left of Nationality:argentine##1
5. Food:peas is on the left of Nationality:brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | peas | onion | lime | watermelon   |
| Nationality   | pakistani  | brazilian     | polish   | argentine |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
Hobby: chess, singing, gardening, dancing
Sport: golf, basketball, tennis, climbing
1. Hobby:dancing == Sport:basketball##1
2. Hobby:chess is on the far right##1
3. Hobby:singing is on the right of Hobby:dancing##1
4. Hobby:dancing is on the right of Sport:tennis##1
5. Sport:basketball is on the left of Sport:golf##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | gardening | dancing | singing | chess    |
| Sport   | tennis    | basketball      | golf | climbing |

